Using this popup, you may specify the sort direction for the current column.  
The sort direction is used only for columns with a non-zero sort sequence.   

To specify a sort direction, scroll to the desired direction, and choose the 
Select menu command. 

	OPTIONS		DESCRIPTIONS
	-------		------------
	Ascending	Sort the data based on this column in ascending order.
	Descending	Sort the data based on this column in descending order.

The menu commands are as follows:

        MENU COMMANDS   SYNOPSIS
        -------------   --------
	Select	        Sort the current column in the specified direction.
			
        Cancel          Return to the Column Options frame without selecting 
			a sort direction.

        Help            Print this message.
